# PY-MP-008 — Digitalización Inicial LM

---

## Description
OCR-based preprocessing module that converts scanned LM PDFs into structured intermediate datasets while preserving page and item relationships.

---

## Key Functions
- OCR extraction of text and numeric fields from scanned PDFs.
- Detection of rows, columns, and item boundaries.
- Dictionary-based recognition of known engineering terms.
- Generation of clean, ordered intermediate files for downstream processing.

---

## Tools
- Python
- Tesseract OCR
- PyMuPDF
- OpenCV
- Pandas

---

## Output
Structured intermediate data reflecting the original document logic and order.
